      "abstract": "Requires the Hawaii Teacher Standards Board to develop an alternative pathway for a visiting international educator permit aligned to the duration of the educator's J-1 visa program.  Repeals 6/30/2031.  Effective 7/1/2050.  (SD1)"
    }
